{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f53092a7bf","title":"给胡志明的复信和关于复信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9258cfedef","index":1,"year":1963,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"951aea151a","index":0,"year":1963,"month":12,"day":26,"articleId":"f53092a7bf"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d20738c862","name":"世界形势","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"9ed3898e7a","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡志明，当时任越南共产党中央委员会主席、越南民主共和国主席。"},{"id":"f2d69f7cac","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"少奇，即刘少奇。小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"4e4b930758","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1bcbd6d05e","type":"title","text":"给胡志明的复信和关于复信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"9ed3898e7a","type":"paragraph","text":"请少奇、小平再阅后，交尚昆办","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"f2d69f7cac","type":"subtitle","text":"毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"4e4b930758","type":"paragraph","text":"廿六日亲爱的胡志明同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"afc7e07c7a","type":"paragraph","text":"几次来信，都已收到，甚为感谢。中苏谈判，几个月后可以开第二次会，目前几个月内还不宜开，因为没有什么新鲜的话好讲。在十一个党会议上共同商定政策以后，中苏就可以开会了。看来不止谈三四次，可能要谈十几次或几十次，谈几年到十几年，才能谈出个有利于革命有利于真正团结的结果来。对此我们是有耐心的。目前国际形势很好，料想你和你的战友们也感觉到了。听说你们的中央全会开得很好，谨致热烈的祝贺。新年将到，敬致贺忧","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"28326260dd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"},{"id":"fdf3ad6073","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年十二月二十七日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf"}],"page":{"id":"7735425ba0","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"f53092a7bf","start":176,"end":177}}}},"__N_SSG":true}